## Visual

A dark celestial poster with gold serif typography frames a glowing dome-like graph boundary over a cliff edge, separating an upper blue network of possibilities from a lower gold network of realized actualities. The central diagram uses nodes, edges, dashed guide lines, and a vertical axis to make the “firmament” read as a mathematical partition rather than a sky object. Lower panels combine numbered argument boxes, a continuous-time quantum walk formula, a small state-transition graph, and an ornate warning box in a scholarly, cosmic, illuminated-manuscript style.
